OL,3,CNewcastle City Council chief Nick Kemp
OL,4,Cresigns amid bullying allegations
OL,6,FThe leader of Newcastle City Council -
OL,7,FNick Kemp - has resigned with
OL,8,Fimmediate effect.
OL,10,FHe had recently been the subject of a
OL,11,Fbullying complaint, but had not
OL,12,Fresponded to the allegations.
OL,14,FIn a statement Councillor Kemp said
OL,15,Frecent events have had a "significant
OL,16,Fand detrimental effect on him and his
OL,17,Ffamily", and he "strenuously denies
OL,18,Fand refutes" any allegations of
OL,19,Fbullying behaviour.
