OL,3,CNewcastle City Council chief Nick Kemp
OL,4,Cresigns amid bullying allegations
OL,6,FHe added: "Allegations have been made,
OL,7,Fand although arrangements are in place
OL,8,Fto prevent disclosure of personal
OL,9,Finformation, details of this
OL,10,Fallegation were disclosed to the media
OL,11,Fbefore the opportunity had been
OL,12,Fafforded to collect evidence to assess
OL,13,Fwhether the claim merited an
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,F"At this time, this decision has not
OL,17,Fyet been made.
OL,19,F"I strenuously deny and refute any
OL,20,Fallegations of bullying behaviour.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
