OL,3,CNewcastle City Council chief Nick Kemp
OL,4,Cresigns amid bullying allegations
OL,6,F"Whilst my advisors and I are firmly
OL,7,Fof the opinion there is no case to
OL,8,Fanswer in this matter, this recent
OL,9,Fdisclosure in parallel with the
OL,10,Fefforts of others to deliberately
OL,11,Fdiscredit and undermine my work, the
OL,12,Fgood work being delivered by certain
OL,13,Felected representatives and this
OL,14,Fadministration, gives rise to pressure
OL,15,Fand stress that is both relentless and
OL,16,Fintolerable.
OL,18,F"The most recent being disclosure of
OL,19,Fconfidential correspondence informing
OL,20,Fgroup colleagues of my ill health, to
OL,21,Fthe press and to the opposition.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
