OL,3,CNewcastle City Council chief Nick Kemp
OL,4,Cresigns amid bullying allegations
OL,6,F"As such, I no longer feel able to
OL,7,Foperate in good faith in the position
OL,8,Fof Leader of Labour Group and of
OL,9,FNewcastle City Council."
OL,11,FHe added that he has resigned as he no
OL,12,Flonger felt able to operate in the
OL,13,Frole of council leader in good faith
OL,14,Fand that his family and health are his
OL,15,Fpriority.
OL,17,FThe council said its thanks to Mr Kemp
OL,18,Ffor his hard work and a new leader
OL,19,Fwill be appointed at a future meeting.
OL,20,FCouncillor Kemp will continue to
OL,21,Frepresent his ward of Byker.
