OL,3,CNewcastle City Council chief Nick Kemp
OL,4,Cresigns amid bullying allegations
OL,6,FDeputy Leader of the Council, Cllr
OL,7,FKaren Kilgour, said: "I would like to
OL,8,Fthank Cllr Kemp for all his hard work
OL,9,Fduring his time as Leader of Council.
OL,11,F"We will not be commenting further
OL,12,Fwhile there is an ongoing council
OL,13,Fprocess."
OL,15,FIt is now for elected members of the
OL,16,Fcouncil to appoint a new Leader of
OL,17,FCouncil at a future meeting of full
OL,18,Fcouncil.
